969fcf1f57e9ca","tid":2051872,"uid":35429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:06:11.000Z","msg":"J less"},{"pid":"1995035422284a415e473657701496c15a9c8012","tid":2051872,"uid":209219,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:09:34.000Z","msg":"陰公 21歲仔就臀虧"},{"pid":"77911cadb8bb89d08bcf8ae8a353d3578cc39dcf","tid":2051872,"uid":35484,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:10:26.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=c6c2669e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精由腎儲藏，而精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。<br />\n每射一次就傷身一次，包括做愛，夢遺（含精量唔多），而節制打Ｊ只不過係延遲你出症狀既時間／嚴重程度。<br />\n<br />\n每人體質唔同，症狀都唔同，以下為最常見：<br />\n早洩，變樣哀，猥瑣，臉色灰暗，自卑冇自信、腰痛<br />\n腦力下降，暗瘡，有口氣，脫髮、耳嗚、任何神經症<br />\n體臭，易怒，夜尿，表達能力差，社交恐懼症，雙眼無神，前列線炎<br />\n<br />\n戒丁必睇資料：<br />\n戒為良藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=4921a5c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a><br />\n戒J 前後對比圖<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.noj1314.258club.com/forumdisplay.php?fid=63\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.noj1314.258club.com%2Fforumdisplay.php%3Ffid%3D63&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=c1e0afb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.noj1314.258club.com/forumdisplay.php?fid=63</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n戒Ｊ需知： <br />\n<br />\n戒Ｊ後３個月內症狀加重／加深屬正常，係戒斷反應<br />\n<br />\n身體恢復過程並唔係直線上升，而係好似過山車咁上下移動，會不斷由壞轉好，好轉壞<br />\n但隨著時間既增長，身體會慢慢恢復，症狀慢慢消失<br />\n<br />\n夢遺唔當破戒，意淫都傷身，睇ＡＶ唔Ｊ一樣咁傷身 ，中醫：心動則精自走<br />\n<br />\n做愛都傷身，所以我地戒Ｊ恢復身體，身體好虧既戒返２年，之後再節制性行為，咁就唔會出症狀，飛翔老師推薦一月2次，就是腎氣充足的情況下，這樣對身體傷害較小。<br />\n<br />\n戒色唔係做和尚，係先禁慾養返好個身體，再同老婆／女友節制性生活，咁就唔會出症狀<br />\n<br />\n叫雞係比打丁更加嚴重既邪淫，如果你忍唔到，寧願你打丁，都唔好叫雞<br />\n<br />\n戒丁期間扑野唔算破戒，但你本身既症狀，唔洗諗住會恢復<br />\n<br />\n戒丁最好既方法就係睇戒色文章，想成功戒Ｊ就將（戒為良藥）睇一次<br />\n學習提升覺悟，覺悟降伏心魔，唔睇（戒為良藥），基本上只係等破戒"},{"pid":"0e11e4fa399659b26990b5a2127d2a74fb5e1a3c","tid":2051872,"uid":358318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98b82856fb6cf754c2e26b31ad969fcf1f57e9ca","tid":2051872,"uid":35429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:06:11.000Z","msg":"J less"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:26:18.000Z","msg":"唔關事好耐無打 之前1個禮拜2次 3次"},{"pid":"191a4335d9bb3734fced81eb37e42389c50478f6","tid":2051872,"uid":40867,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"497cd57b4d42fd2fccfa4cc284dcedcba7f2888f","tid":2051872,"uid":77973,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T05:55:15.000Z","msg":"試下2日唔飲水, 應該唔會再屙"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:37:43.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n應該訓左唔會醒"},{"pid":"f4c539380df4a1d97cfd38cee006d2836e4a16a3","tid":2051872,"uid":192078,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ff3a131e4d928daa1429d40650ac0d9942a717d0","tid":2051872,"uid":15605,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T05:55:41.000Z","msg":"下半身截肢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:51:40.000Z","msg":"高位截肢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9043c8e26f561abd949ff2757767e27210dc372","tid":2051872,"uid":3559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:21:52.000Z","msg":"同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下星期排左去照超聲波"},{"pid":"f8001cb2cc65b10bf76cd8ef932233058022f86d","tid":2051872,"uid":358318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9043c8e26f561abd949ff2757767e27210dc372","tid":2051872,"uid":3559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:21:52.000Z","msg":"同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgm